title: Braumix - un remix di Braum!

embed.description: Domics and Jomm took Braum's voice and remixed it. Mother always said, "Stand behind Braum!" Domics: http://www.youtube.com/user/d0mics Jomm http://www.youtube.com/user/flashj0mm **Created in collaboration with Riot Games**

body:
